traits.locale_text: "Госпожа Кибелла, вы весьма уверенно действуете в незнакомых местах. А ведь вы всю жизнь провели на корабле".

languages.text: "Mistress Kibellah, you move with the utmost confidence in unfamiliar places. And yet, until now, you have spent your entire life on a voidship."

languages.text: «Maestra Kibellah, se mueve con una confianza absoluta en lugares desconocidos, a pesar de haber pasado toda su vida hasta ahora en una nave del vacío».
languages.original_text: "Mistress Kibellah, you move with the utmost confidence in unfamiliar places. And yet, until now, you have spent your entire life on a voidship."

languages.text: 「キベラ様、不慣れな場所でもしっかり自信を持って動かれるのですね。にもかかわらず、あなた様はずっとヴォイドシップで生きてこられた」
languages.original_text: "Mistress Kibellah, you move with the utmost confidence in unfamiliar places. And yet, until now, you have spent your entire life on a voidship."

languages.text: “绮贝菈女士，你的举止看起来充满自信，不过你从没来过这个地方。事实上，你不久之前从没离开过旗舰。”
languages.original_text: "Mistress Kibellah, you move with the utmost confidence in unfamiliar places. And yet, until now, you have spent your entire life on a voidship."

languages.text: "Meisterin Kibellah, Ihr bewegt Euch an fremden Orten mit erstaunlicher Selbstsicherheit. Und doch habt Ihr bis jetzt Euer ganzes Leben auf einem Raumschiff verbracht."
languages.original_text: "Mistress Kibellah, you move with the utmost confidence in unfamiliar places. And yet, until now, you have spent your entire life on a voidship."

languages.text: « Maîtresse Kibellah, vous vous déplacez avec assurance même dans les lieux qui vous sont inconnus, et pourtant, vous avez passé toute votre vie sur un vaisseau. »
languages.original_text: "Mistress Kibellah, you move with the utmost confidence in unfamiliar places. And yet, until now, you have spent your entire life on a voidship."

languages.text: "Kibellah Hanım, aşina olmadığın yerlerde son derece kendine güvenerek hareket ediyorsun. Ancak şimdiye kadar tüm yaşamını bir sancak gemisinde geçirmişsin."
